Method Detail

onChangePublicPorts

void onChangePublicPorts(Set<ForwardPort> ports,
                         ForwardPortCallback cb)
Called when Fred's list of public ports changes, and just after loading the plugin.

Parameters:
ports - The set of ports that need to be forwarded from the outside world through the NAT or firewall.
cb - Callback to be called with success/failure of each forward. Some plugins may return a probabilistic success e.g. with UP&P.
